• Member, Consultative Committee for the Ministry of Home Affairs
• Member, Committee on Commerce (May 2008 - May 2009)
• Elected to Rajya Sabha (April 2008)', '• Term 1: 10/04/2008-09/04/2014 (Jharkhand, Independent & Others)
• Term 2: 10/04/2014-09/04/2020 (Jharkhand, Independent & Others)
• Term 3: 22/06/2020-21/06/2026 (Andhra Pradesh, Yuvajana Sramika Rythu Congress Party)')
